ITT Corp said it received a final 400mln dlr payment for its telecommunications joint venture with&lt;Alcatel NV>, settling all accounts in the venture.    The company had previously said it was due to receive the400 mln dlr payment.    Alcatel NV was formed last year when ITT and &lt;Cie Generaled'Electricite> of France merged their telecommunicationsbusiness. ITT received a 37 pct interest in Alcatel and 1.3billion dlrs in cash, including today's payment. Reuter&#3;